Package: rTwChannel
Type: Package
Title: Twitter channel stream analitics
Version: 0.2
Date: 2016-08-04
Author: Alfonso Crisci <a.crisci@ibimet.cnr.it>, Valentina Grasso
    <v.grasso@ibimet.cnr.it>
Maintainer: Alfonso Crisci <a.crisci@ibimet.cnr.it>
Description: This package performs analitics on Twitter datastreams obtained by
    a structured query by using Twitter search/streaming API. The form of data are
    frames of data where significant elements of tweets are reported.
